Board of Health v. Valentine. (Supreme Court, General Term, Second Department. December, 1891.) Action by the board of health of the village of Hew Rochelle against Eugenia Valentine.

Argued before Barnard, P. J., and Dykman and Pratt, JJ.

Ho opinion. Motion denied. See 11 N. Y. Supp. 112; 14 N. Y. Supp. 941.
